# DB ↔ Frontend CRUD Coverage Fix

## Changes Made

### 🔴 Critical Fixes (2 files)

**API response key mismatches** — These caused [DailyDelivery](file:///d:/programming/web/fullstack/11gawe/src/types/index.ts#266-319) and [OutstandingPayment](file:///d:/programming/web/fullstack/11gawe/src/types/index.ts#321-336) data to never load on the frontend.

| File | Before | After |
|---|---|---|
| [route.ts](file:///d:/programming/web/fullstack/11gawe/src/app/api/memory/daily-delivery/route.ts) | `deliveries: records` | `dailyDeliveries: records` |
| [route.ts](file:///d:/programming/web/fullstack/11gawe/src/app/api/memory/outstanding-payment/route.ts) | `payments: records` | `outstandingPayments: records` |

### ⚠️ Missing Fields (1 file)

Added **15 DB fields** to [daily-delivery route.ts](file:///d:/programming/web/fullstack/11gawe/src/app/api/memory/daily-delivery/route.ts) POST/PUT handlers:

`analysisMethod`, `terpal`, `insurance`, `basePriceNotes`, `poMonth`, `product`, `arriveAtPol`, `commenceLoading`, `completeLoading`, `startDischarging`, `completeDischarged`, `podQuantity`, `lossGainCargo`, `invoiceAmount`, `specContract`

